---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about Awesome CloudNatives and how to contribute">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">About Awesome CloudNatives</h1>

      <div style="background: var(--color-bg-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Our Mission</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          The DevOps, Cloud, and Cloud-Native ecosystem is vast and growing every day. With hundreds of amazing
          content creators, thought leaders, and practitioners sharing their knowledge, it can be overwhelming
          to discover who to follow and learn from.
        </p>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.8;">
          <strong>Awesome CloudNatives</strong> aims to solve this by creating a centralized, community-curated
          directory of influential voices in the space. Whether you're looking for Kubernetes experts, AWS gurus,
          DevOps practitioners, or Platform Engineering pioneers - you'll find them all here.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="background: var(--color-bg-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">What Makes Someone "Awesome"?</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          We look for people who:
        </p>
        <ul style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-left: 1.5rem;">
          <li>Actively create content (blogs, videos, talks, courses, podcasts)</li>
          <li>Share knowledge and help educate the community</li>
          <li>Have a consistent public presence for at least 6 months</li>
          <li>Focus on DevOps, Cloud, Cloud-Native, or related technologies</li>
          <li>Demonstrate genuine expertise and community engagement</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="background: var(--color-bg-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">How to Contribute</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          This is a <strong>community-driven project</strong>. We welcome contributions from everyone!
        </p>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <a href="https://github.com/nimeshmora/awesome-cloudnatives/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md" class="cta-link">
            üìñ Read Contributing Guidelines
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/nimeshmora/awesome-cloudnatives/issues/new?template=add-influencer.yml" class="cta-link">
            ‚ûï Suggest an Influencer
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/nimeshmora/awesome-cloudnatives" class="cta-link">
            ‚≠ê Star on GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="background: var(--color-bg-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 2rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Self-Submissions Welcome</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.8;">
          Are you a content creator in the DevOps/Cloud/Cloud-Native space? We encourage self-submissions!
          If you meet the criteria above, please don't hesitate to add yourself to the directory.
          Just be honest about your contributions and impact.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem; padding: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          Built with ‚ù§Ô∏è by the cloud-native community
        </p>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem;">
          Powered by <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Astro</a>
          and <a href="https://pagefind.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Pagefind</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .cta-link {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      background: var(--color-bg-tertiary);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--color-primary);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .cta-link:hover {
      background: var(--color-primary);
      color: white;
      transform: translateX(4px);
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
